# Deployment & Development Workflow

## Local Development
- Use PNPM per [package.json](mdc:package.json) scripts.
- Configure Next.js via [next.config.ts](mdc:next.config.ts).
- Type safety via [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json).
- Development server: `pnpm dev` with Turbopack support.

## Build & Deployment
- Deploy on Vercel; ensure environment variables are configured in the platform UI.
- Avoid committing secrets or personal information to the repository.
- Keep analytics integrations (e.g., Vercel Analytics) enabled where configured.

## Quality
- Run linters and type checks before pushing.
- Keep bundle size in check; prefer server components by default.
- Use ESLint configuration in [eslint.config.mts](mdc:eslint.config.mts).

